plementing loadClass method**\\n\\nI'm considering implementing a synchronized loadClass method. If the class name isn't CLEAN_UTIL_CLASS_NAME, I'll return the super version. I need to find a loaded class or load it if it isn't already loaded. If I resolve, I'll call resolveClass. For finding classes, if it's only for the target, I’ll use getParent().getResourceAsStream for loading bytes. But what if the parent is null? It’ll throw an IOException. I also need to manage Method.invoke calls, which might add extra dynamic access call sites. I wonder how the TCK will track this!\", \"thinkingSignature\": \"{\\\"id\\\":\\\"rs_01d3ce057da11f900169fe55c5ccd0819d8e6c5d7699e5c1f7\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"reasoning\\\",\\\"encrypted_content\\\":\\\"gAAAAABp_lXWqNR2W4thTF5UVgPrquzv3ZRZiINfr0pBjlS7mI9Sl4H01oHfvMSl0QawB7MLfeAp-9lT1Bwbndtqjl84LRt5gli5yUDdqz5oliVpjC88GrKaEP3VSeEnWvKWBRl6SmATy8LX_beILnYYAd9b-wsW1ll6Fahds3nvJhRQWlzqDhOL37wICVcOJMu7kPmhvIEd6IP7K6_L01l4t8X-Cx4e2fDBFY1GNfX3w2_ddQaQ-9WyItwmUqqguQOyw9vebi45YfzIdke2gXAd_FmPcnSH_DyA_7sQ2ZgEOqRGL9rwUFEVRyRu8IKaSY8ODUctZQC8t0J4xHOGtWGLX5Zg4KpBYCfItWnwt3mNevQGmPszmk1AM3wttASSfztfQ7ty7ZgNU_lCZK8oEcDLytSzH43JjpRL1TaLRed6UQBUlvD4IDhRAadO4FgiJoT6TWP247lcPYL7zMAmCC_fyfZr8xq66Sr2YrFVmZIoxmYpzYUsutc6BBUuUoqQhZhx3j3nSaSW78SQ5n5Xsk76mVJdczbmy2hr332y-tlH7sq0vwfCJNHOjE7mtVwAGc4RfcXYoUf6QNuznisqJ98wxkO42cp6aMyFNYzjYfIlmMt98hXPiuix5YnlBktcO4H8UZCUUC0nxOB5Rh_lwm1Hpikx82oMyCKZLLgxj3EWpC8lbTHIzlneDrcSUgMxoP4-Tf16JkSajzFPVAE6wQIhzeNuaXwwv-EVg6WMI2auNKA-sxebcQK_MquP8EoCOLkkmM1afgAGkBvoh_5QlIbjoDIY7xTTLmrogPPI6Mha2B3Rj-GrkaV34UeM1u33_zKZopfbRFrBjz_RJRRPXnnqWWdMb2_R3zDigpnIauj2KdspkYPr_mnXSJ6I2mfXwgdA8Oa5SKrvNqtoSBIl93Oq0PQ8UmtNSAfn9d4U5NzmI2UsN6mQQYMagxIFsusDLQwEucKao6ZXq4BG6QjXnY4Gby6pRklr-01Pq90aNdtqsHXatiXPlVWjUXkRhINBPXNY-83vJeyDKDgsn2pTWPTTrB3-3wslkSEiNqOn5A2VXvN062ac3JYlQYWYQGk1mZcqEeCdvAg-75eacJlkw0RQa8JdX5p1opk2xEN_eSnL2yQ5mFzBm3L2hwBrP15u-xTFhNTl2uGduOBJt0wsSOPPvC2P2vrOFNLD8STYg9c0vIJ0QPgU25Igvoa4zzhOUw88sU3ezyarFyRcrgJghpTxCIyXZzeXG-l3kpx